ey respect the safe area boundaries. I need to verify whether these safe area properties have changed in .NET 9 or 10, since I want to give accurate guidance on what's currently supported rather than relying on older information.","outputTokens":1071,"requestId":"7FFA:36C261:62CB5BB:6BAFFAF:69F15A04"},"id":"54653739-5c8d-4dd3-9c8b-0dddada189c7","timestamp":"2026-04-29T01:08:39.957Z","parentId":"32eed7bc-7365-4e3d-bc7c-8471dbdc357f"}
